    "body": "Well before we can find an answer we have to agree on the question: what's the purpose or missing statement of `requirements.txt` anyway? Is it _supposed_ to be just what `grpcio` depends on? Is it _supposed_ to be everything necessary to build, test, package, and deploy `grpcio`? Or something else?\r\n\r\nI thought I might find the answer [here](https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/user_guide/#requirements-files) or [here](https://pip.readthedocs.io/en/1.1/requirements.html) but neither seems to come out and say."
